    <para id="id7545802">Examining the feedback network in Figure 8:</para>
    <para id="id10167495">Feed back voltage <figure id="id10203708"><media id="id10203708_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics26-2884.png" id="id10203708__onlineimage" height="34" width="209"/></media></figure></para>
